<L>__{exterior the private airliner flying day}
<A>__{superimposed over a map that traces a course from new york city to venice, italy.}
<T>__{dissolve to:}
<L>__{exterior venice boat landing day}
<A>__{indy and brody disembark from the water bus onto the boat landing as other gondoliers steer their boats in the water.}
<C>__{indy}
<D>__{ah, venice...}
<C>__{brody}
<D>__{yes. uh, how will we recognize this doctor schneider when we see him?}
<C>__{indy}
<D>__{i don't know. maybe he'll know us.}
<A>__{suddenly a woman comes up to him. attractive features. blonde hair. eyes that are bright and intelligent.}
<C>__{elsa}
<D>__{doctor jones?}
<C>__{indy}
<D>__{yes?}
<C>__{elsa}
<D>__{i knew it was you}
<A>__{she looks at him with an appraising expression that is brazenly flirtatious.}
<C>__{elsa}
<D>__{you have your father's eyes.}
<A>__{indy is instantly attracted to her.}
<C>__{indy}
<D>__{and my mother's ears. but the rest belongs to you.}
<C>__{elsa}
<D>__{looks like the best parts have already been spoken for.}
<A>__{indy grins, enjoying the repartee. the woman turns to brody, who tips his hat.}
<C>__{elsa}
<D>__{marcus brody?}
<C>__{brody}
<D>__{that's right.}
<A>__{the woman, dr. elsa schneider, extends her hand to brody.}
<C>__{elsa}
<P>__{(introducing herself)}
<D>__{doctor elsa schneider.}
